    "chemicalDescription": [
      "r-Saccharomyces/Methionyl s-Ocean Pout Type-3 Ice Structuring Protein HPLC 12 is a single chain recombinant protein produced by fermentation in Saccharomyces. The starting gene is synthetically produced to be identical to Type-3 Ice Structuring Protein HPLC 12 which is found in the ocean pout, Zoarces americanus, with the initiation code for methionine. The protein contains 66 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
    ],
